Package: betRBall
Title: An R package for football betting calculations and visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("William", "Wiik", email = "william.wiik@hotmail.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of tools for modeling, simulating and analyzing football matches and betting markets. 
    Includes functions for expected goals, team strength estimation, and value bet detection.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    scales,
    stats,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr
Suggests:
    roxygen2,
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    dplyr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/willewiik/betRBall
